systemd is quite vague about it.

```C
        e = getenv("LISTEN_PID");
        if (!e) {
                r = 0;
                goto finish;
        }

        r = parse_pid(e, &pid);
        if (r < 0)
                goto finish;

        /* Is this for us? */
        if (getpid_cached() != pid) {
                r = 0;
                goto finish;
        }
```

From `sd-daemon.c`

